  <refnamediv>
    <refname>ann_FF_Std_batch</refname>
    <refpurpose>standard batch backpropagation.</refpurpose>
  </refnamediv>  
  
<refsection>
    <title>CALLING SEQUENCE</title>
    <para>W = ann_BP_Std_batch(x,t,N,W,lp,T[,af,ex])
     </para>
  </refsection>  
<refsection>
    <title>PARAMETERS</title>
    <para>   This function have same parameters as ann_FF_Std_online except for:
  
 ex   string representing a valid Scilab program sequence, executed after
      each epoch trough execstr.
     </para>
  </refsection>  
<refsection>
    <title>Description</title>
    <para>   Returns the updated weight hypermatrix of a feedforward ANN, after
  training with a given set of patterns, T times. The algorithm used is
  standard batch backpropagation.
     </para>
  </refsection>  
 
